column5: FYI...By the look of things as of today, John will not be at Lost Bay. If anyone wants to talk...email me please. [email protected]
Welcome back. How have you been?
I have been through a lot since LBR. Much of it not good that's why I gave my e-mail address. Feel free to use it...Rose
Rose, Good to see you back on the board......you mention that much of the recent past hasn't been good, so I know many of us here hope the future will be brighter for you. Rich B
thank you so much. I will be fine. Just wanted to let people know that Lost Bay is misrepresenting John being at camp.
Hi Rose, great to see you back on boardThank you,Larry Mac
It's good to have you back, Rose, as you can see above, you were missed! Bill Krejca
Hello Bill, How many books have you sold? A "boat" load I hope! Thanks for the greeting and I hope this note finds you and your family well...Rose
We've missed you Rose! I hope things get better for you and John both.
Doing well, thanks for asking. Family is fine, son is again going with me in July. Great to hear from you! Bill
